Class IntegerList

java.lang.Object
IntegerList
Direct Known Subclasses:
ImmutableList, PrimeList, SortedList, UniqueList
public class IntegerList extends Object
Resizable array structure for integers. Internal array doubles at 100% capacity and halves at 25% capacity.
Version:
0.2
Author:
Cameron Bost
